                        Conditional Statements
Thre are 3 types of conditional Statements
1. when
2. failed_when
3. changed_when
We can club any module with conditional Statements


                        when conditional Statements
> It is like if coonditional statement in other languages.
> It works or execute any task if condition is true.
> Condition/expression can be form with comparision, membership, test and logical operators.

